import './mapsvg.css';

function MapSvg() {
  return (
    <svg width="90%" viewBox="0 0 1367 713" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
        <rect x="405" width="385" height="385" fill="url(#pattern0)" class="pointer"/>
        <rect y="56" width="643" height="426" fill="url(#pattern1)" class="pointer"/>
        <rect x="312" y="239" width="1055" height="474" fill="url(#pattern2)" class="pointer"/>
        <defs>
        <pattern id="pattern0" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
        <use xlinkHref="#image0_147_84" transform="scale(0.0012987)"/>
        </pattern>
        <pattern id="pattern1" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
        <use xlinkHref="#image1_147_84" transform="translate(0 -0.00950872) scale(0.000792393 0.00119603)"/>
        </pattern>
        <pattern id="pattern2" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
        <use xlinkHref="#image2_147_84" transform="scale(0.000473934 0.00105485)"/>
        </pattern>
        <image id="image0_147_84" width="770" height="770" xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"/>
        <image id="image1_147_84" width="1262" height="852" xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"/>
        <image id="image2_147_84" width="2110" height="948" xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"/>
        </defs>
    </svg>

  )
}

export default MapSvg;
